These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, fishing, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, spy, time-travel, scientific
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, rowing, cricket, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, trike, bus, train
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##8
 2. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
 3. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8
 5. the person driving the tram is not to the right of the person driving the tram##8
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 8. the person watching scientific movies is between the person driving the trike and the person who's sport is rowing##2
 9. the person driving the train is the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
13. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
14. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person driving the bus##1
15. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person who's sport is rowing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | gardening     | puzzles   | video-games | fishing |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | scientific   | action   | time-travel  |
| Sport         | rowing  | cricket  | swimming  | climbing |
| Transport     | tram    | bus | trike     | train    |

