.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, fanta, 7up
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, cabbage, onion, artichoke
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, metal, jazz, blues
4 different pets are kept: goat, snake, bird, rat
 1. the fan of jazz is between the owner of the goat and the fan of metal##2
 2. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
 3. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3
 4. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the owner of the rat##8
 5. the owner of the goat is not to the left of the fan of metal##8
 6. the person eating artichoke is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
 7. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
 8. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of punk is the owner of the snake##1
10. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
11. the owner of the goat is not to the left of the fan of jazz##8
12. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
13. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
14. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
15. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
17. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the fan of metal##8
18. the person eating cabbage is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
19. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | mirinda | fanta | 7up  | cola  |
| Food          | artichoke     | cabbage | blueberry | onion  |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | jazz  | blues | punk |
| Pet           | bird | rat | goat    | snake  |

