 3. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the left of the person watching family movies##8
 7. the fan of ambient is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
11. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the left of the fan of soul##8
12. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

