 5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person eating avocado##8
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the photographer##1
10. the journalist is the person who's sport is badminton##1
11. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the right of the person eating pomegranate##8
12. the bartender is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
13. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
14. the journalist is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
15. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an odd position##4

