 4. the firefighter is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking almond-milk##7
 7. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
 8. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is dancing##7
 9. the software-developer is on the far left or far right##3
10. the engineer is not to the left of the engineer##8
11. the software-developer is on the far left##1
12. the project-manager is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
14. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
15. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
