There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, tea, lemonade, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, rock, country, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, ice-hockey, skateboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, subway, train, motorbike
 1. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
 4. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
 6. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 8. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##8
 9. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
10. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the fan of rock##8
11. the fan of country is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the person driving the motorbike is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola   | hot-chocolate     | lemonade    | tea |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | disco      | country     | rock     |
| Sport         | basketball | ice-hockey  | skateboarding     | rowing  |
| Transport     | trike     | train | motorbike | subway     |

