.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, water, fanta
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, board-games, rock-climbing, traveling
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, rock, jazz, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, polish, american, australian
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the australian##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
 3. the person drinking fanta is the fan of rock##1
 4. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
 6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the left of the fan of techno##8
 7. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 8. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the american##3
 9. the polish is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
10. the fan of jazz is not the spanish##6
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
12. the australian is on the left of the person drinking water##1
13. the fan of punk is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
14. the spanish is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | lemonade      | fanta  | water | almond-milk        |
| Hobby         | traveling | board-games   | card-games   | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | rock   | jazz    | techno      |
| Nationality   | polish   | australian | american   | spanish    |

