.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, 7up, fanta
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, architect, security-guard, journalist
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, cat, bird, hamster
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, ship, helicopter, car
 1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 2. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the architect##8
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person drinking water##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
 6. the person driving the car is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the journalist is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
 8. the security-guard is on the far right##1
 9. the architect is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
10. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
12. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
13. the person driving the helicopter is not to the left of the journalist##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate          | water | 7up        | fanta    |
| Job         | journalist | videographer   | architect | security-guard  |
| Pet         | bird           | guinea-pig     | hamster       | cat  |
| Transport   | car            | helicopter   | ship     | bus |

