.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, milk, cola
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, drawing, dancing, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, scientist, freelancer, journalist
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, car, ship, bike
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person drinking milk##6
 2. the pilot is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
 3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the car##1
 4. the pilot is not to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
 5. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the freelancer##5
 6. the person driving the ship is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the freelancer##8
 9. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
10. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the journalist##7
11. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage    | milk        | 7up        | hot-chocolate        | cola   |
| Hobby       | drawing      | traveling      | woodworking | dancing |
| Job         | journalist | freelancer | scientist     | pilot  |
| Transport   | ship          | scooter      | car     | bike  |

