.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, camping, puzzles, magic-tricks
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, coach, photographer, accountant
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, sports, disaster, thriller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, ambient, pop, funk
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the fisherman##8
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the fan of funk is somewhere to the right of the fan of pop##5
 4. the accountant is the person watching thriller movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the photographer##6
 6. the person watching documentary movies is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8
 7. the person watching sports movies is not to the left of the photographer##8
 8. the photographer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
 9. the fan of pop is in an even position##4
10. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
11. the person watching documentary movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the photographer and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
13. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks    | puzzles   | photography   | camping |
| Job           | fisherman | coach    | photographer | accountant    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | documentary | sports     | thriller    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | pop      | ambient         | funk     |

 